knowledge/gold_standards/rayleigh_benard_convection.yaml:15:      evidence_ref: "Docker E2E 2026-04-16 produced Nu=10.5 matching ref exactly; convergence OSCILLATING but Nu-value stable. STATE.md §Known Limitations confirms this contrasts with DHC Ra=1e10 which does NOT satisfy this precondition."
