knowledge/gold_standards/turbulent_flat_plate.yaml:16:  reference_correlation_context: "ref_value 0.00420 at x=0.5m uses the Blasius laminar similarity solution Cf=0.664/√Re_x evaluated at Re_x=25000. Blasius is the exact self-similar solution of the Prandtl BL equations under ZPG with no-slip wall; it is exact for laminar flow at all Re_x below transition. Adapter runs simpleFoam with turbulenceProperties laminar; no wall-function model is active."
