knowledge/gold_standards/lid_driven_cavity.yaml:63:  reference_correlation_context: "Ghia, Ghia & Shin 1982, J. Comput. Phys. 47, 387-411 — Table I Re=100 column is the canonical reference for 2D lid-driven square-cavity flow. u_centerline reference values below are Ghia Table I interpolated to the harness's 17-point uniform y grid (DEC-V61-030 Q-5 Path A closure, 2026-04-21)."
